# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Docker
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile
**/Dockerfile.*
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/docker-compose*.yaml

# Build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/artifacts
**/publish
**/out

# IDE / editors
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userprefs
**/.editorconfig.user

# Test outputs
**/TestResults
**/*.trx
**/*.coverage
**/*.coveragexml
**/coverage.cobertura.xml
**/coverage.opencover.xml

# Test projects (not part of the runtime image)
tests/

# NuGet
**/*.nupkg
**/*.snupkg
**/packages
**/project.lock.json
**/project.fragment.lock.json
**/*.binlog

# Local / secret configuration
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/appsettings.*.Local.json
**/secrets.json
**/*.pfx
**/*.env
**/.env.*

# Dev-only launch profiles (not used inside containers)
**/Properties/launchSettings.json

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# Repository docs (not needed inside the image)
**/*.md
**/LICENSE
**/CHANGELOG*
